snippet.title: Spaceship Hunters gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Spaceship Hunters is a chaotic couch co-op shoot-em-up for 4 players. Working as a crew, fight your way through the worst criminals the universe has to offer.

Available soon on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1819290/Spaceship_Hunters

For additional info chat with me on discord: https://discord.gg/CQSpaFhsCf
